<plot>Released shortly before Buddy Clark's death in a plane crash, and playing theatres after his death, this Screen Snapshots has Clark as the narrator who introduces many of the nation's top radio disc jockeys of the time. Similar to the "Disc Jockeys,U.S.A" entry in this series, meaning that Staub either found disc jockeys interesting,or shot more footage than he could use the first time around.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?482194</url></doc>
